lead_paragraph: Celtic will have to make the seemingly impossible possible to progress in the Champions League, manager Brendan Rodgers said ahead of Tuesday's clash at Borussia Moenchengladbach.

headline.print_headline: Celtic Must Make Impossible Possible in Champions League-Rodgers
